original_title: Before They Were Wrestling Stars: CM Punk
overview: Want to know all about professional wrestler CM Punk's life before he made a name for himself? Featuring some of his earliest bouts, this intriguing video traces the experiences that shaped Punk's identity and helped him become a success in the ring. Determined to make it to the top of his sport, Punk crisscrossed America to compete in countless independent wrestling matches before hitting pay dirt.
title: Before They Were Wrestling Stars: CM Punk
